<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Quizfluence</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <section class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">About Quizfluence</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Revolutionizing learning through intelligent, AI-powered quizzes that adapt to your knowledge level and learning style.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    At Quizfluence, we believe in transforming education through cutting-edge AI technology. Our platform generates dynamic, personalized quizzes that challenge and engage learners across various subjects and skill levels.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    By leveraging advanced artificial intelligence, we create intelligent question sets that adapt in real-time, ensuring a truly personalized learning experience.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">AI-Powered Learning</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain text-blue-600 mr-4 text-2xl"></i>
                        <span>Intelligent question generation</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-blue-600 mr-4 text-2xl"></i>
                        <span>Adaptive difficulty levels</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot text-blue-600 mr-4 text-2xl"></i>
                        <span>Machine learning insights</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-12 mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">How We Work</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-magic text-4xl text-blue-600"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">AI Question Generation</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Our AI analyzes vast knowledge bases to create unique, challenging questions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-cubes text-4xl text-green-600"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">Adaptive Learning</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Questions dynamically adjust based on your performance and knowledge.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-pie text-4xl text-purple-600"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">Personalized Insights</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Receive detailed analytics to track your learning progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="text-center bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Get In Touch</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We're always excited to hear from our users and potential collaborators.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
                <a href="mailto:quizfluence@gmail.com" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i> Email Us
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 transition flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-comment-dots mr-2"></i> Contact Form
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>